name: Corporal Derdram
Lore: 'Member of Imperial Intelligence, Internal Security division. Assigned by IntSec to Executor. Responsible for physical safety of Imperial personnel against Rebel saboteurs.',
Text: 'Power +1 when at any Executor site. While at Detention Block Corridor, cancels game text of Detention Block Control Room. May use 1 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take one IT-O or Hypo into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.',
